This layer provides support deploying devices that connect with peridio.com

For more information visit peridio.com

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://github.com/openembedded/meta-openembedded.git
  layers: meta-oe
  branch: kirkstone

  URI: https://github.com/meta-erlang/meta-erlang
  branch: kirkstone

  URI: https://github.com/fwup-home/meta-fwup
  branch: master

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-peridio layer to your build


I. Adding the meta-peridio layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-peridio'

Configuring
============

Peridiod can produce firmware output when as a post process to the image creation.
Configure your image to execute this command automatically by adding the following
to your image recipe:

```text
require recipes-core/images/peridio-image-complete.inc
```
